{"tid":1544392,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發有圖］大埔有狗拉完車主後搜車 直接揸車主架車走","createTime":"2019-09-05T14:17:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T23:04:37.000Z","uid":275293,"like":66,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"8a94e1b8fde229c696ec61960131dc5bdd74de70","tid":1544392,"uid":275293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:17:56.000Z","msg":"Sorry P牌第一次開post，但係有一手料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大約九點黑警係大埔富亨截停一架白色私家車，並聲稱九龍發生意外，懷疑車主車內有攻擊性武器（伸縮棍），將車主拘捕至大埔狗屋。<span style=\"color: gold;\">趁車主唔係現場搜查車輛</span>，打開車尾箱搜查，放置不明物品於其車尾箱內（有可能係原本車內物品，但有冇順手放其他唔屬於車主嘅物品就不得而知）。最後，一名黑警上車<span style=\"color: red;\">直接揸走</span>！<br />\n完全冇程序可言！！放咩落去都唔知啦！<br />\n有議員問過班黑警點處理，佢哋話無可奉告！<br />\n（搜車前嘅野係我係現場問街坊，搜車時及之後係我親眼望住，如果之前嘅事發經過有錯漏麻煩補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fz5XspQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffz5XspQ.png&h=e6311198&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aTAwwRw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaTAwwRw.png&h=62b95c09&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b85013203cabac1d427545ef15ca1bd976422885","tid":1544392,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:18:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人<br />\n約定你<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aTJem7g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaTJem7g.jpg&h=c2ef69f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e91jFMP.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe91jFMP.gif&h=6056e7b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n九月八日 星期日<br />\n絕對和理非<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n12:00pm <br />\n遮打集合<br />\n(歡迎遲到，好過無到) <br />\n<br />\n2:00pm<br />\n<ins>美國駐港澳總領事館</ins> <br />\n為《香港人權及民主法案》請願</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">聽熟首歌未？<br />\n到時一齊唱 ：</span></span><br />\n<br />\nOh, say can you see,<br />\nBy the dawn's early light,<br />\nWhat so proudly we hailed,<br />\nAt the twilight's last gleaming?&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPWMy7Rpk5Bo&d=t4s0zgtGzRvDs5iH%2BzYNWPRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=4f3e1e66\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">揮國旗(<span style=\"color: blue;\">美國</span>x<span style=\"color: red;\">香港</span>) ：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6CAXjTX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6CAXjTX.jpg&h=00eeedf1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人，九月八日見</span>"},{"pid":"fe0ed0c94089bbd3675e838bbe606b4ebf7f0854","tid":1544392,"uid":275293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:18:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f696d8d52624b60eccf48fa7e806c2606777b415","tid":1544392,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:18:52.000Z","msg":"推啦"},{"pid":"5328f8c64295b8767dc1c47b3731cd8a0c8a212b","tid":1544392,"uid":275293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:19:15.000Z","msg":"有大埔手足可以去大埔狗屋支援"},{"pid":"447174584d8b44518daae1ed78f5fb00de085000","tid":1544392,"uid":221004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:19:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b40a0aceea249904b6023e2222e332401c5e9f4f","tid":1544392,"uid":106472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:20:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b5b0609fd21f4f188a5f3c4d112957f1f40f90eb","tid":1544392,"uid":305794,"like":0,"dislike